Class FunctionNode

    • com.bigdata.bop.CoreBaseBOp

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BOp, IValueExpressionNode, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubqueryFunctionNodeBase

    public class FunctionNode
extends ValueExpressionNode
    AST node for anything which is neither a constant nor a variable, including math operators, string functions, etc. The FunctionNode arguments are the ordered list ValueExpressionNodes that are the arguments to the SPARQL function.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Mike Personick

    Serialized Form
